<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <title>WaterFlowsEast.com 的邮箱验证</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    table {
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }

    #topbar {
      width: 16.67%;
      background-color: #285a2e;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: top;
      padding-top: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    #topbar a {
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", "Helvetica", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 96px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #e6e6e6;
      padding: 3px;
      border: 8px solid #e6e6e6;
    }

    #topbar a:hover {
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      color: #285a2e;
      border: 8px solid #bbb;
    }

    #main {
      background-color: #eff8f0;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", "Helvetica", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #285a2e;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", "Helvetica", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    p a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #285a2e;
      padding-left: 5px;
      padding-right: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tr>
      <td id="topbar">
        <a href="http://waterflowseast.com">流</a>
      </td>
      <td id="main">
        <h1>邮箱验证</h1>
        <p>点击<a href="<%= email_confirm_url(confirm_token: @user.confirm_token) %>">这里</a>进行验证，若点击无效，可复制以下链接到浏览器</p>
        <p><%= email_confirm_url(confirm_token: @user.confirm_token) %></p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
